DefaultReaderConfiguration.fullDescription: Collects events about services running on the F5 appliances.

file.toolTipText: Directory or path to read from

string.toolTipText: Hostname of the nDepth appliance to receive log data

integer.toolTipText: Port number of the nDepth appliance to receive log data

select.toolTipText: Data routing (normalized alerts to Manager and/or raw data to nDepth)

integer.toolTipText: Number of seconds between log reads

FastPattern.description: 2, ServiceWarning: ntpd_initres, couldn't resolve, giving up

FastFormatter.format: Couldn't resolve "$6", giving up on it
Couldn't resolve $6, giving up on it

FastPattern.description: 8, ServiceStop: ntpd, ntpd exiting on signal
9, ServiceWarning: snmpd, Connect to master agent successfully
10, ServiceWarning: snmpd, snmpd subagent is up
11, ServiceWarning: subsnmpd, subsnmpd exits due to license change
FastPattern.pattern: \s\S*subsnmpd\S*: subsnmpd exits due to license change

FastPattern.description: 16, ProcessWarning: pidof, can't get program name
FastPattern.pattern: pidof\[\d+\]: can't get program name from \S+
(?:auditd|ntpd)\[\d+\]: (?:Audit daemon rotating log files|kernel time sync enabled)

FastPattern.description: 22, ConfigurationTrafficAudit: Received SNMP packet(s) from UDP
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ snmpd\[\d+\]: Received SNMP packet\(s\) from UDP: \[[\d.]+\]:\d+
xpand\[\d+\]: Raid: (?:in raidCardExist|card information not received)

FastPattern.description: 25, ServiceInfo: routed; sending ping, found the node, Ping received
27, ServiceWarning: xpand; Raid Hardware recognition failed
28, ServiceWarning: xpand; Failed to init raid
FastPattern.pattern: xpand\[\d+\]: RAID monitoring: Failed to init

FastPattern.description: 29, ServiceWarning: modprobe; FATAL: Could not open
30, ServiceInfo: dhclient; No {DHCPOFFERS received, working leases}

FastPattern.pattern: dhclient: DHCPDISCOVER on \S+ to [-\w.]+ port \d+ interval \d+

FastPattern.description: 33, ServiceWarning: snmpd, lookup_vswitch; failed Not found
35, ServiceWarning: snmpd, load_lags; no port config found
FastPattern.pattern: \s\S*snmpd\S*: load_lags: no port group configs found

FastPattern.description: 37, ServiceWarning: ntpd_intres, host name not found
39, ServiceWarning: root, vsantraced is not started
NullAlert: snmpd, Received broken packet. Closing session.
FastPattern.pattern: snmpd\[\d+\]: Received broken packet. Closing session.

FastPattern.description: NullAlert: named drops (being caught by bind.xml)
NullAlert: init: Trying to re-exec init
NullAlert, dropped daemon messages: bcm56xxd, checkcert, iControlPortal.cgi, ntpd
